                <Property name="rows" type="int" value="5"/>
                <Property name="text" type="java.lang.String" value="Created By :- Dihh Mart Solutions Pvt Ltd&#xa;&#xa;Dihh Mart IT Solution Development Center is a dynamic&#xa; tech hub driven by innovation and precision. Our expert &#xa;team&#x2014;Pranav Purohit(Project Manager), Omkar Singh &#xa;(Backend Developer), Avi Jadoun (Frontend Developer), &#xa;Dipesh Patil (AI &amp; Data Engineer), and Manav Jain &#xa; (Blockchain &amp; Cloud Specialist)&#x2014;collaborates to deliver &#xa;cutting-edge IT solutions. We specialize in AI, blockchain&#xa;, cloud, and custom software development, helping &#xa;businesses accelerate digital transformation. With a&#xa; culture built on creativity, teamwork, and technical&#xa; excellence, we strive to craft secure, scalable,&#xa; and intelligent systems that empower organizations&#xa; to grow in today&#x2019;s fast-evolving digital world.&#xa;&#xa;"/>
              </Properties>
